OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather grey start but cloud
OL,6,Fwill lift and break throughout the
OL,7,Fmorning allowing some spells of
OL,8,Fsunshine to develop. A few showers
OL,9,Fwill also develop but many will remain
OL,10,Fdry. Feeling fresher than of late.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FApart from the odd shower it
OL,13,Fwill be a dry evening with some late
OL,14,Fsunshine. Overnight cloud will tend to
OL,15,Fincrease with the breeze also
OL,16,Ffreshening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
