OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FAny early brightness quickly
OL,6,Freplaced by a band of rain which will
OL,7,Fspread eastwards throughout the
OL,8,Fmorning. The rain will be heavy at
OL,9,Ftimes, give a rather wet afternoon.
OL,10,FBreezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA
OL,13,Fchangeable middle of the week with
OL,14,Fsunshine and scattered heavy showers
OL,15,Finterspersed with a longer spell of
OL,16,Frain on Wednesday. Temperatures near
OL,17,Faverage for early June.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
